title: Vikings S03 special Secrets of the Vikings WS.XviD-err0001
description:
Vikings S03 special - Secrets of the Vikings 

In this special, Michael Hirst, the creator and writer of the TV series Vikings, together with a number of scholars, provide some historical background for the show. In particular, the special focuses on shield maidens, the great halls and Viking ships. 

History.ca has a series of 6 clips with the same name which appears to include more information and footage. The material on History.ca is dated Feb 5, 2015 and a variety of scenes from the show are shown, so I have labeled it as a season 3 special.

This aired on History HD in Canada. Like all of my releases to date, the source is an analog rip, so the quality is, at best, something like A8 V8. 

To leave comments/questions for me, use thepiratebay or kickass.
